{"tid":2513753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美防長指應對未來戰爭須科技領先和全球軍事整合","createTime":"2021-05-02T19:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T19:48:17.000Z","uid":187112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ede467083fb62fec75cd63e7203965dfd4e6543","tid":2513753,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:03:29.000Z","msg":"美國國防部長奧斯汀表示，美國必須為未來的戰爭做好準備，它與以往的舊戰爭全然不同。它將依靠量子計算和人工智能等尖端技術。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯汀在夏威夷的美軍太平洋司令部，出席印太司令交接，發表上任後首次重要政策演說，呼籲利用科技領先以及更好的全球軍事行動整合，達到「快速理解、快速決策、以及快速行動」。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯汀說，科技快速發展，代表美軍確保國家安全的範疇，除了海陸空，還有太空和網絡都起了重大變化，美國需要新的能力和靈活性，應對未來的戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\n而離任印太司令部司令的戴維森則表示，毫無疑問，中國共產黨力求以一種新的秩序，取代自由開放的國際秩序，這是具有中國特色，中國國力比國際法更重要的秩序。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588773-20210501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588773-20210501.htm&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=477c6031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588773-20210501.htm&h=ed48246b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588773-20210501.htm</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未來美國會大大發展人工智能、量子計算、edge computing。<br />\n香港就繼續炒炒賣賣。"},{"pid":"ef01b154cac53cad61f49250d28b3024945b3db2","tid":2513753,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"fake news<br />\n敗燈明明係投共"},{"pid":"ef22a5a151282b8c2bf1f965918ed5f29630f280","tid":2513753,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef01b154cac53cad61f49250d28b3024945b3db2","tid":2513753,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"fake news<br />\n敗燈明明係投共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"官方資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.militarytimes.com/news/pentagon-congress/2021/05/02/defense-secretary-austin-calls-for-new-vision-for-american-defense/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.militarytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpentagon-congress%2F2021%2F05%2F02%2Fdefense-secretary-austin-calls-for-new-vision-for-american-defense%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=a18e3b46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.militarytimes.com/news/pentagon-congress/2021/05/02/defense-secretary-austin-calls-for-new-vision-for-american-defense/</a> <br />\n<br />\nAustin mentioned no specific potential flashpoints for conflict in the Indo-Pacific region but said the U.S. must develop a new vision of defense that takes greater advantage of new technologies, including quantum computing, artificial intelligence, and edge computing, which he described as a framework that allows data to be processed while it&rsquo;s being collected, and to absorb and share it instantaneously."},{"pid":"6ec7f7bda6bd5adb7f4e5d59824620f6f4bdc34f","tid":2513753,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef01b154cac53cad61f49250d28b3024945b3db2","tid":2513753,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"fake news<br />\n敗燈明明係投共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:23:55.000Z","msg":"係囉 cctoy話敗燈上任後會奶共 美國變咗一個既省架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國人你地同我聽住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ea8140af585dc8397d54e79e53e214c227a292","tid":2513753,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec7f7bda6bd5adb7f4e5d59824620f6f4bdc34f","tid":2513753,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef01b154cac53cad61f49250d28b3024945b3db2","tid":2513753,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"fake news<br />\n敗燈明明係投共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T19:2